template.description: This template is to annotate an entire index. The documents are ingested according to a flag to indicate whether they have been annotated or not. Workflow also includes logging components, component to update source_index annotation flag to true (once the doc has been annotated) and a component to measure the time spent in the medcat processor.
template.name: Annotate_All_Docs

labels.label:
This workflow is the annotation of all documents.
Extra logging has been added: files from retry/failure are written to an ES index.
An extra processor (Replace text) has also been added to remove the No Break Space unicode character, because of which files were stuck in the medcat retry queue.
This workflow also implements an 'annotation_status' flag which is used to keep track of the documents successfully annotated, and a 'medcat_processing_time' attribute to track the time the file has spent in the medcat processor. The workflow has been modified to only allow one file at a time to enter the Medcat processor to get accurate timing for processing (otherwise processing time will include the time spent waiting in the queue).
